Package: drawsneeded
Type: Package
Title: Estimates the number of samples needed to ascertain that the defect rate does not exceed a treshold
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Crist-Jan", "Doedens",
      email = "cjd@chance-matters.nl",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: In an audit of a file of like items, we might use sampling to establish
   an estimate of the overall defect rate.
   Computes an estimate of the necessary number of sampled items given a posited defect rate,
   and a maximally acceptable defect rate.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
